{"tid":445600,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]去應酬時，我著低胸連身裙，比老闆摸我個胸......點算好？","createTime":"2017-10-23T13:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T16:28:51.000Z","uid":19334,"like":22,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"64c4146311d0746c4b0b700981385dee9c1cca05","tid":445600,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:57:04.000Z","msg":"因為公司有一個重要既晚宴，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老闆叫出席既員工都著得靚啲，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我就著左一條Deep V既緊身既連身裙，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有露小小事業線既，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n保守得黎有點性感，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋我覺得我胸型係最靚，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我都幾鍾意條裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但當晚出席時，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老闆唔知係咪已經飲大左，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一見到我就好興奮咁抱住我，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我果下已經有d想推開佢，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢攬到實一實，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁佢隻手就有意無意咁掃落我個胸到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要笑淫淫咁，感覺好似抽水！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果日有影到幾張自拍(50正評有圖)！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322744d8554a278233a1a537b7783d328689d38b","tid":445600,"uid":21634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:58:03.000Z","msg":"關人撚事"},{"pid":"f2e3835362981b7b38cd15b711c95938700216a1","t